txt.en: 'A new face is it? Well, stranger, you're most welcome to join us in return for a story!'
'We'll need to finish all this food before they'll bring out the deserts, and I daresay I'm equal to the task!'
'I hear queer things are going on in Bree! I'm glad Staddle will always stay the same quiet place.'
'You must try one of the biscuits, they're lovely.'
